name: We are all artists but most of us don't know
description:
Piece #5 of the collection:
I'm not your therapist but I'd like to cheer you up with my dorky art

The series focuses on the fragility of the inner world and brings up topics that we often find in our long journey on earth. 

#5
We are all artists, but we got lost in rules. Society programs us to disconnect from our creativity so that we become merely obedient cold pieces of humans.
